OL,5,C15%'
OL,7,FEating two slices of ham a day could
OL,8,Fincrease the risk of developing type 2
OL,9,Fdiabetes within the next 10 years by
OL,10,F15%, a study has suggested.
OL,12,FData from nearly two million people `
OL,13,Fanalysed by a team led by the
OL,14,FUniversity of Cambridge ` has found
OL,15,Fthat consuming 100 grams of
OL,16,Funprocessed red meat a day `
OL,17,Fequivalent to a small steak ` was
OL,18,Fassociated with a 10% higher risk of
OL,19,Fdeveloping the condition.
