OL,7,FResearchers said the findings,
OL,8,Fpublished in the journal The Lancet
OL,9,FDiabetes and Endocrinology, back the
OL,10,Frecommendations to cut down meat
OL,11,Fintake.
OL,13,FSenior author Professor Nita Forouhi,
OL,14,Fof the University of Cambridge's
OL,15,FMedical Research Council (MRC)
OL,16,FEpidemiology Unit, said: "Our research
OL,17,Fprovides the most comprehensive
OL,18,Fevidence to date of an association
OL,19,Fbetween eating processed meat and
OL,20,Funprocessed red meat and a higher
OL,21,Ffuture risk of type 2 diabetes.
