OL,7,FFor the study, the researchers
OL,8,Fanalysed data from 31 study cohorts
OL,9,Finvolving 1.97 million people across
OL,10,F20 countries through InterConnect ` a
OL,11,Fproject funded by the European Union
OL,12,Fto understand more about diabetes and
OL,13,Fobesity across different populations.
OL,15,FThey found 50 grams of processed meat
OL,16,Fa day ` equivalent to two slices of
OL,17,Fham ` was associated with a 15% higher
OL,18,Frisk of type 2 diabetes within a
OL,19,Fdecade.
