OL,5,C15%'
OL,7,FBut they said the link between eating
OL,8,Fpoultry, such as chicken, turkey, and
OL,9,Fduck, and type 2 diabetes remains
OL,10,Funcertain and needs further
OL,11,Finvestigations.
OL,13,FThe researchers said the InterConnect
OL,14,Fdata allowed the team to "more easily
OL,15,Faccount for different factors, such as
OL,16,Flifestyle or health behaviours, that
OL,17,Fmay affect the association between
OL,18,Fmeat consumption and diabetes".
