OL,7,FIt also included people usually under-
OL,8,Frepresented in scientific research
OL,9,Fwith cohorts from countries in the
OL,10,FMiddle East, Latin America and South
OL,11,FAsia alongside Europe and the US.
OL,13,FProfessor Nick Wareham, director of
OL,14,Fthe MRC Epidemiology Unit and a senior
OL,15,Fauthor on the paper, said the data
OL,16,F"allowed us to provide more concrete
OL,17,Fevidence of the link between
OL,18,Fconsumption of different types of meat
OL,19,Fand type 2 diabetes than was
OL,20,Fpreviously possible".
