OL,7,FCommenting on the study, experts said
OL,8,Fthat while the research cannot show
OL,9,Fhow or why red and processed meat
OL,10,Fintake increases the risk of type 2
OL,11,Fdiabetes, the findings align with the
OL,12,Fcurrent healthy eating recommendations.
